data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath 2 car garage in basement. Hardwood floor in LR, hall & primary bedroom, roof over deck, fenced in backyard, storage shed, finished room in the basement.  This lovely home is centrally located to Exit 1.  Located close to retail shops and grocery stores.  All bedrooms are on the 1st floor of the house.  The basement has a beautiful bonus room.  Interior has been freshly painted.  IT'S A MUST SEE!!!!!!!!!!
